metadata.description: The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.

metadata.cwe: CWE-89: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')
metadata.description: App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.

metadata.description: Files may contain hardcoded sensitive information like usernames, passwords, keys etc.

This App uses SSL certificate pinning to detect or  prevent MITM attacks in secure communication channel.
App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.
App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.

playstore_details.title: Life Fitness Connect App
playstore_details.description:
Life Fitness Connect gives you the freedom to take control of your workouts. Whether you’re hitting the gym or exercising at home, our app is designed to enhance your fitness journey.


Strength Workout Library

Get started quickly with our extensive library of pre-built workouts or customize your own from over 500 exercises.


Create Your Own Exercises

Can't find the exercise you need? No problem. Add your own exercises to your personal library.


Automatic Cardio & Strength Workout Tracking

Effortlessly track your cardio workouts by scanning the QR Code on Life Fitness Cardio equipment, or tap to connect on compatible strength equipment.  All your results will be automatically recorded in the app.


Advanced Workout Statistics

For the data enthusiasts, view detailed metrics for each exercise, including personal bests and distances completed.


Workout Scheduler

Stay committed to your fitness goals by scheduling your workouts in advance. Never miss a session again.


Customizable Rest Timer

Say goodbye to using multiple devices. Our built-in rest timer keeps you on track and ensures you maximize your workout efficiency.


Download Life Fitness Connect now and transform your fitness journey!
